{"tid":575790,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"【影片曝光】他們對蔣中正靈柩潑紅漆　高喊：去除支那威權","createTime":"2018-02-28T11:52:18.000Z","updateTime":"2018-02-28T13:48:25.000Z","uid":171257,"like":18,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":7,"replies":[{"pid":"933eff8de45d9637948cbc2c20c24f055fc0bc81","tid":575790,"uid":171257,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-02-28T11:52:18.000Z","msg":"上午10點10分左右，有10多名民眾將紅油漆藏在衣服內闖入，並朝停在裡面的蔣介石棺柩潑灑紅漆，駐守現場的憲兵官立刻上前制止，甚至拉起標語布條高喊訴求。<br />\n <br />\n潑漆民眾在臉書上表示，他們是一群關切公義、主張落實轉型正義的青年，「將象徵受難者鮮血的紅漆，潑灑在獨裁者停靈的棺柩」。<br />\n <br />\n國防部對此則表達遺憾，並譴責非理性的行為。（二二八淋雨抗議，他有什麼冤？）<br />\n <br />\n<a href=\"http://www.upmedia.mg/news_info.php?SerialNo=36051?=p\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fwww.upmedia.mg%2Fnews_info.php%3FSerialNo%3D36051%3F%3Dp&d=mZqk7%2F5Ln6xCEo9p7kBXjS7PofNJLCAwyGXsi6MH%2FEQ%3D&h=0e17fae6\" target=\"_blank\">http://www.upmedia.mg/news_info.php?SerialNo=36051?=p</a><br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://youtu.be/-6OedsxAZSc\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fyoutu.be%2F-6OedsxAZSc&d=mZqk7%2F5Ln6xCEo9p7kBXjS7PofNJLCAwyGXsi6MH%2FEQ%3D&h=9f625ca9\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://youtu.be/-6OedsxAZSc</a>"},{"pid":"d82104fca7e6c14d22638fede4de7fe9d3f8a29d","tid":575790,"uid":59898,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-02-28T11:54:39.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"8152173f764421723f8684e92276084fde1f01d1","tid":575790,"uid":26451,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-02-28T12:24:51.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"f120c3f9056d3dca9b75a4f5fb3a7c37f9bc26a3","tid":575790,"uid":63017,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-02-28T12:41:05.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"d6e0a06bb390dd2a78bc3e153ce84b34e465b720","tid":575790,"uid":55552,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-02-28T13:24:30.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":